## Continue

The **continue** statement skips to the next iteration.

```javascript
for (let i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
  if (i === 5) {
    continue;  // Skip when i is 5
  }
  console.log(i);
}
```

blocks.code:
for (let i = 1; i <= 10; i++) {
  if (i % 2 === 0) {
    continue;  // Skip even numbers
  }
  console.log('Odd number:', i);
}
